model.agent.humanAgent

Class AatomHumanAgent

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.map.MapComponent

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CircularShape, DirectlyUpdatable, SimulationObject, Updatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OperatorAgent, Passenger

    public abstract class AatomHumanAgent
extends HumanAgent
    A AatomHumanAgent is a human that can move around on a map. It contains two main elements: a StrategicModel and a OperationalModel. The StrategicModel determines the higher level plans of the agent. It for instance determines its goals and the preferred speed it wants to walk. The OperationalModel determines the lower level interactions with the surroundings. The HumanAgent acts autonomously and bases its decisions on its surroundings and its internal (high level) state.
    Author:
    S.A.M. Janssen
